cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on analyzing the effectiveness of domain adaptation in neural machine translation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves analyzing the capacity of different components of the system, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves training and adaptation of neural networks, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves analyzing the embedding space, which can be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
